{"tid":1038741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯遭起訴勢「加監」","createTime":"2019-02-27T01:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T04:30:19.000Z","uid":199590,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc202a1e6c6a6fa390932134049e7cc428f4de1","tid":1038741,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:55:25.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6VKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=1d066fd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】歐洲足協周二宣佈經過調查後，正式起訴皇家馬德里後衛沙治奧拉莫斯故意在比賽中領黃牌，意味該西班牙悍將面臨多停賽1場的處分。<br />\n<br />\n32歲的沙治奧拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）於早前歐聯16強首回合對阿積士（皇馬勝2:1）末段技術性犯規，此舉被指是故意領取黃牌，令他肯定錯過下周上演的次回合比賽，如今他面臨被判罰多停賽1場的處分，周四將有裁決。<br />\n<br />\n拉莫斯曾重申對阿積士所領獲的黃牌，是身不由己：「我沒選擇餘地，那是在88分鐘一次非常危險的反擊，而比賽形勢均等。」他續解說：「這解釋為我說如果不清楚領牌後會停賽是騙人，正如我知沒選擇而去犯規。而這是我所指在足球，你得作出困難的選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n至於主帥蘇拿利也曾為其解畫：「根據他的說話，他表明只是故意犯規。他被問了一個很狡猾的問題，你們記者自有方法。無論如何，他已經解釋了。」"},{"pid":"7a04d1da651f7ecdce0c0fb01ec77ba59bb5bfae","tid":1038741,"uid":83094,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5f6de8f1321291c97d5a17add090858cf1606ba","tid":1038741,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class